  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hameau du Borsat apartments are well located with skiing only a stones throw away, and a selection of bars and restaurants nearby. The apartments are ideal for keen skiers who want good value accommodation without any frills but with convenience of immediate access to the slopes and ability to ski once the lifts open.</p>
<h2>Skiing on your doorstep</h2>
<p>These compact apartments are just 200 metres from the ski lifts in Tignes Val Claret, giving you excellent access to the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a> and the extensive slopes on offer.  Start your day in Val Claret and warm up your legs on the gentle slopes before heading up to the Grand Motte glacier for more challenging red runs - the other areas of Tignes and Val d'Isere are within easy reach too, plus at the end of the day you can virtually ski back to the door. </p>
<h2>Self catered apartments</h2>
<p>Each of the Studio apartments we offer offer simple and compact accommodation in the centre of Val Claret. These apartments have a open plan living room and kitchenette with microwave, bathroom and an alcove with two additional beds,  plus most apartments have a balcony so you can enjoy the resort views. As these are self catered apartments, you have the flexibility to enjoy meals from the comfort of your apartment or head into the resort centre to have a meal in one of the lovely restaurants often serving Savoyard specialities such as fondue or raclette. The centre of Val Claret with a number of bars. restaurants and shops is just a short walk from the residence - perfect for a self catered stay in Tignes.</p>]]></description>
