  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Great location in Val Claret with skiing to the doorstep</li>
<li>The Bollin lift goes up by the side of the residence so in the morning you just ski down to this lift or on to the Grand Motte funicular or Les Lanches or Tichots chairlifts.</li>
<li>The ski school meeting point and nursery slopes are at the bottom of the Bollin chairlift.</li>
<li>There is a choice of bars and restaurants all within a few minutes' walk of the residence. </li>
</ul>]]></locationDescription>
